    Convert Interval to Vector

    as.vector.interval.Rd

    Convert Interval to Vector

    # S3 method for class 'interval'
as.vector(x, ...)

    Arguments

    x

    An interval object.

    ...

    Additional arguments to be passed to or from methods.

    Value

    A vector representation of the interval.
